{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Do3R6XazLiGNEbA9RJGCKr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the problem now! The stack trace shows:\n\n```\n\"at com.amazonaws.auth.InstanceMetadataServiceCredentialsFetcher.getCredentialsEndpoint(InstanceMetadataServiceCredentialsFetcher.java:58)\"\n\"at com.amazonaws.auth.InstanceMetadataServiceCredentialsFetcher.getCredentialsResponse(InstanceMetadataServiceCredentialsFetcher.java:46)\"\n\"at com.amazonaws.auth.BaseCredentialsFetcher.fetchCredentials(BaseCredentialsFetcher.java:112)\"\n\"at com.amazonaws.auth.BaseCredentialsFetcher.getCredentials(BaseCredentialsFetcher.java:68)\"\n\"at com.amazonaws.auth.InstanceProfileCredentialsProvider.getCredentials(InstanceProfileCredentialsProvider.java:166)\"\n\"at com.amazonaws.auth.EC2ContainerCredentialsProviderWrapper.getCredentials(EC2ContainerCredentialsProviderWrapper.java:75)\"\n```\n\nThe AWS SDK is trying to fetch credentials from the EC2 Instance Metadata Service (IMDS), which means the keystore credentials aren't being picked up. The SDK is falling back to `InstanceProfileCredentialsProvider` instead of using the configured keystore.\n\nThe root issue is that the repository-s3 plugin isn't loading the `s3.client.default.access_key` and `s3.client.default.secret_key` from the keystore, so the AWS SDK times out trying to reach the EC2 metadata endpoint. This could be happening because the keystore credentials weren't loaded properly, the `reload_secure_settings` call didn't work, or the keystore entries weren't present when Elasticsearch started.\n\nActually, I think I've found it — the keystore file itself is stored in the container's ephemeral filesystem at `/usr/share/elasticsearch/config/elasticsearch.keystore`, not on the persistent volume. When the pod restarted after the StatefulSet patch, the keystore was reset to empty, so the S3 credentials we added earlier are gone.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4296,"cache_read_input_tokens":67206,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4296},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ac5cff4-d409-4ac3-8f10-c278d889fd74","uuid":"f8a4db72-75a5-48f4-a32a-ff74588a1a56","request_id":"req_011CcLRYNy31drfmFzECAzYp"}
